arChildNodes.szComment: Meshif has been RUN THROUGH. A DEAD CULTIST lies nearby, apparently slain by Meshif.
Meshif painfully reaches behind his back. To our surprise, he takes out a BOTTLE OF BOOZE. He takes a swig.
Meshif hands the bottle to Lorath who accepts, grief heavy.
Lorath takes a long drink. Finished, he tucks the bottle under Meshif’s arm.
Lorath stands, pushing through grief and fatigue. He strides to the CAMEL and prepares to leave.
